  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/3d486c79dbda76ee6aa6db38284f65ef.poster.avif?t=1770099996\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/3d486c79dbda76ee6aa6db38284f65ef.webm?t=1770099996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/3d486c79dbda76ee6aa6db38284f65ef.mp4?t=1770099996\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Heard of the Story? is a cosy medieval city-building simulation game with intelligent and quirky villagers who think, reason, and tell their own unique tales. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is about forging your own medieval town, community, and relationships with procedural characters that really feel alive, self-aware, and grounded in your world. Embark on an adventure with them to transform a few sticks and pebbles into a beautiful prospering town from the ground up. Alternatively, simple sit back and watch as your townsfolk discover their passions, spread rumours, or divulge captivating stories with you and between each other.  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/4c0c0b3f738630c1d5cbb12613547b95.avif?t=1770099996\" width=600 height=113 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/c1fa2b5f33ce412885569b8c11636c50.poster.avif?t=1770099996\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/c1fa2b5f33ce412885569b8c11636c50.webm?t=1770099996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/c1fa2b5f33ce412885569b8c11636c50.mp4?t=1770099996\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/bbb3bc755dfa80108a3be78071e1e1ed.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> Explore the landscape to find and gather the resources you need in order to build your town. Craft your way up to an expert, perhaps you can be their blacksmith?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/a353680193cbccd563f9873e0bf100fe.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> Develop a town organically by architecting your roads or structures without a grid. Beautify the surroundings with decorations whilst your villagers spice up their gardens.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/262102b25f96f4c960980cb646b6cbf3.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> Each building changes the life of your villagers one step at a time. Could the Lion & Crow be your friend's next favourite tavern? Or the Chiselled Bellows the smithy they discover themselves in?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/da6767274bd86c3614282616b358da0f.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> Strengthen your reputation by constructing the right amenities, enough fields and accommodation, and entice foreigners to join - grow without a limit!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/dc4cad4bb55c86ac0f25e37166a303fd.avif?t=1770099996\" width=600 height=113 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/bc7addbb974e47f90e45aa6944baffb7.poster.avif?t=1770099996\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/bc7addbb974e47f90e45aa6944baffb7.webm?t=1770099996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/bc7addbb974e47f90e45aa6944baffb7.mp4?t=1770099996\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/7a4598012b765c6b24d1773a67078745.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> Villagers are autonomous and independent. Apart from starting new construction projects, they can do anything you can. Each has their own interests, goals, achievements, needs, and traits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/ea652883a23f75c778a193a0e516afb7.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> Talk to villagers to discover their lore, (sometimes) get helpful advice, or learn about their conspiracy theories. Your learnings are jotted down in your journal as you uncover more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/7b9544bfa96dfa7d6f10c6dcebb0ae19.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> Each interaction they have with the world forms an experience which shapes their personality. Reveal how they changed and evolved through listening to their quirky stories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/3f7fa9150a01ccef5e0a7f94affb0376.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> Deepen the mutual bond by helping them with their troubles. Or don't, and tell them they look ugly instead - we won't judge! (but villagers may)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/e2836d7859c5a420e013e4052a3a87ca.avif?t=1770099996\" width=600 height=113 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/9a6de95cf9f585d041474edd00c5c1d8.poster.avif?t=1770099996\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/9a6de95cf9f585d041474edd00c5c1d8.webm?t=1770099996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/9a6de95cf9f585d041474edd00c5c1d8.mp4?t=1770099996\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/e3d3351fb0f8de622cbc5b6a6b41e04e.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> Cooperate with your townsfolk as they help construct new buildings or trade with them to get the items you need.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/41007f514b8376bc9d288674be3ba93d.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> Watch villagers specialise into different skilled crafts like carpentry or horticulture. Unlock your society's potential by making sure they have all the tools they need to prosper.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/e0249c8cc27ff0ebc08f3863d760bbcd.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> When your collective skills don't cut it, merchants and markets can assist you by bringing what you need - at a price. Be careful not to blow your savings on luxurious goods!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/7e8b1494106fea6a9d4686eb5302087a.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> Just like you, villagers can talk to each other, build their own relationships (or start their own beef), and make their own exchanges. As they pass on information, they form an emergent interconnected team.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/03db86bb5a7a3f3b2c570d51430fc1dd.avif?t=1770099996\" width=600 height=113 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/17795224e695c83794964e1db37aa6de.poster.avif?t=1770099996\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/17795224e695c83794964e1db37aa6de.webm?t=1770099996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/17795224e695c83794964e1db37aa6de.mp4?t=1770099996\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/ea1068b7bf37aef7e888341a065c65f7.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> Each map is randomly generated making every playthrough even more unique. Whether you want to build in a valley or a flatland, in a forest or the mountains, the choice is yours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/192391dcad3ac98feadd8e1948317eb9.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> Find cute, scottish-highland inspired cows loitering around different corners and draw them into your barns to tame them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/5f3b8cd370e055a7fb53d16a52bbb4ce.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> World details are also unique to each world, with each having its own regions, towns, family histories. Perhaps you’ll find your rival's sibling joining you as you expand the town.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/aae6a68e8b7c36e6c2ec1a3466b145fd.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> As time passes, the sun will rise, the stars will show, and the seasons will change. Witness colours and atmosphere shift around you as spring gradually gives way to winter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/1f13bf60abe5a7b5a65b89acbd6b201a.avif?t=1770099996\" width=600 height=113 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/7f903d313aff2af61fa9ed9bf91f93ad.poster.avif?t=1770099996\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/7f903d313aff2af61fa9ed9bf91f93ad.webm?t=1770099996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/7f903d313aff2af61fa9ed9bf91f93ad.mp4?t=1770099996\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep warm with a fireplace during winter, or find a colourful place to frolic amidst long grass and arrays of countless flowers during summer. This game is designed to be cosy and stress-free; there are no timed tasks, no harsh penalties, and no combat putting your town at risk. You can challenge yourself to grow a huge town, or play at your own pace and stick to a small cottagecore village, with a few friendly faces.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/3d486c79dbda76ee6aa6db38284f65ef.poster.avif?t=1770099996\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/3d486c79dbda76ee6aa6db38284f65ef.webm?t=1770099996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/3d486c79dbda76ee6aa6db38284f65ef.mp4?t=1770099996\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Heard of the Story? is a cosy medieval city-building simulation game with intelligent and quirky villagers who think, reason, and tell their own unique tales. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is about forging your own medieval town, community, and relationships with procedural characters that really feel alive, self-aware, and grounded in your world. Embark on an adventure with them to transform a few sticks and pebbles into a beautiful prospering town from the ground up. Alternatively, simple sit back and watch as your townsfolk discover their passions, spread rumours, or divulge captivating stories with you and between each other.  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/4c0c0b3f738630c1d5cbb12613547b95.avif?t=1770099996\" width=600 height=113 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/c1fa2b5f33ce412885569b8c11636c50.poster.avif?t=1770099996\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/c1fa2b5f33ce412885569b8c11636c50.webm?t=1770099996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/c1fa2b5f33ce412885569b8c11636c50.mp4?t=1770099996\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/bbb3bc755dfa80108a3be78071e1e1ed.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> Explore the landscape to find and gather the resources you need in order to build your town. Craft your way up to an expert, perhaps you can be their blacksmith?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/a353680193cbccd563f9873e0bf100fe.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> Develop a town organically by architecting your roads or structures without a grid. Beautify the surroundings with decorations whilst your villagers spice up their gardens.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/262102b25f96f4c960980cb646b6cbf3.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> Each building changes the life of your villagers one step at a time. Could the Lion & Crow be your friend's next favourite tavern? Or the Chiselled Bellows the smithy they discover themselves in?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/da6767274bd86c3614282616b358da0f.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> Strengthen your reputation by constructing the right amenities, enough fields and accommodation, and entice foreigners to join - grow without a limit!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/dc4cad4bb55c86ac0f25e37166a303fd.avif?t=1770099996\" width=600 height=113 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/bc7addbb974e47f90e45aa6944baffb7.poster.avif?t=1770099996\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/bc7addbb974e47f90e45aa6944baffb7.webm?t=1770099996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/bc7addbb974e47f90e45aa6944baffb7.mp4?t=1770099996\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/7a4598012b765c6b24d1773a67078745.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> Villagers are autonomous and independent. Apart from starting new construction projects, they can do anything you can. Each has their own interests, goals, achievements, needs, and traits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/ea652883a23f75c778a193a0e516afb7.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> Talk to villagers to discover their lore, (sometimes) get helpful advice, or learn about their conspiracy theories. Your learnings are jotted down in your journal as you uncover more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/7b9544bfa96dfa7d6f10c6dcebb0ae19.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> Each interaction they have with the world forms an experience which shapes their personality. Reveal how they changed and evolved through listening to their quirky stories.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/3f7fa9150a01ccef5e0a7f94affb0376.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> Deepen the mutual bond by helping them with their troubles. Or don't, and tell them they look ugly instead - we won't judge! (but villagers may)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/e2836d7859c5a420e013e4052a3a87ca.avif?t=1770099996\" width=600 height=113 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/9a6de95cf9f585d041474edd00c5c1d8.poster.avif?t=1770099996\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/9a6de95cf9f585d041474edd00c5c1d8.webm?t=1770099996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/9a6de95cf9f585d041474edd00c5c1d8.mp4?t=1770099996\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/e3d3351fb0f8de622cbc5b6a6b41e04e.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> Cooperate with your townsfolk as they help construct new buildings or trade with them to get the items you need.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/41007f514b8376bc9d288674be3ba93d.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> Watch villagers specialise into different skilled crafts like carpentry or horticulture. Unlock your society's potential by making sure they have all the tools they need to prosper.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/e0249c8cc27ff0ebc08f3863d760bbcd.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> When your collective skills don't cut it, merchants and markets can assist you by bringing what you need - at a price. Be careful not to blow your savings on luxurious goods!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/7e8b1494106fea6a9d4686eb5302087a.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> Just like you, villagers can talk to each other, build their own relationships (or start their own beef), and make their own exchanges. As they pass on information, they form an emergent interconnected team.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/03db86bb5a7a3f3b2c570d51430fc1dd.avif?t=1770099996\" width=600 height=113 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/17795224e695c83794964e1db37aa6de.poster.avif?t=1770099996\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/17795224e695c83794964e1db37aa6de.webm?t=1770099996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/17795224e695c83794964e1db37aa6de.mp4?t=1770099996\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/ea1068b7bf37aef7e888341a065c65f7.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> Each map is randomly generated making every playthrough even more unique. Whether you want to build in a valley or a flatland, in a forest or the mountains, the choice is yours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/192391dcad3ac98feadd8e1948317eb9.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> Find cute, scottish-highland inspired cows loitering around different corners and draw them into your barns to tame them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/5f3b8cd370e055a7fb53d16a52bbb4ce.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> World details are also unique to each world, with each having its own regions, towns, family histories. Perhaps you’ll find your rival's sibling joining you as you expand the town.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/aae6a68e8b7c36e6c2ec1a3466b145fd.webp?t=1770099996\" width=20 height=20 /></span> As time passes, the sun will rise, the stars will show, and the seasons will change. Witness colours and atmosphere shift around you as spring gradually gives way to winter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/1f13bf60abe5a7b5a65b89acbd6b201a.avif?t=1770099996\" width=600 height=113 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/7f903d313aff2af61fa9ed9bf91f93ad.poster.avif?t=1770099996\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/7f903d313aff2af61fa9ed9bf91f93ad.webm?t=1770099996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1881940/extras/7f903d313aff2af61fa9ed9bf91f93ad.mp4?t=1770099996\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep warm with a fireplace during winter, or find a colourful place to frolic amidst long grass and arrays of countless flowers during summer. This game is designed to be cosy and stress-free; there are no timed tasks, no harsh penalties, and no combat putting your town at risk. You can challenge yourself to grow a huge town, or play at your own pace and stick to a small cottagecore village, with a few friendly faces.</p>",
